      <p>The addition of Vitamin D is a thoughtful formulation choice. An estimated 42% of American adults are vitamin D deficient, and low vitamin D status is independently associated with elevated cortisol, depressed mood, and impaired immune function. By combining ashwagandha with vitamin D, Goli addresses two of the most common nutritional deficiencies affecting stress resilience in a single serving. At $0.32 per serving with 60 servings per container, this product also delivers strong value relative to its branded extract quality.</p>

