      <p>Nutrafol occupies a unique position in the supplement market. Originally known for its clinically studied hair growth supplements, the brand has expanded into stress management with a multi-adaptogen gummy that combines ashwagandha with <strong>shatavari</strong> (an Ayurvedic adaptogen traditionally used for hormonal balance and reproductive health) and <strong>rhodiola rosea</strong> (a Scandinavian adaptogen with published evidence for fatigue reduction and cognitive performance under stress). The theoretical framework is broad-spectrum adaptogenic support: rather than targeting cortisol alone, the formula aims to support multiple stress response pathways simultaneously.</p>

